data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This expansive 1-level residence offers a modern open concept with immense curb appeal and a backyard retreat for entertaining! The great room is being repainted this week. Trane 5 ton Air Conditioner replaced in July of 2018. New pool pump in 2017. New hot water heater a few years back. Conveniently situated in a family-friendly neighborhood, this home is situated close to schools, shopping, and entertainment. Don't miss this one!
